          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-1" n="1">Dear Sir I think tis Doubly hard</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-2" n="2">Your Ears and Doors shou'd both be Barr'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-3" n="3">Can any thing be more unkind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-4" n="4">Must I not see Cause you are Blind</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-5" n="5">Methinks a friend at night shou'd Cheer you</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-6" n="6">A friend that Loves to see and hear you</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-7" n="7">Why? am I rob'd of that Delight</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-8" n="8">When you Can be no Loser by't</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-9" n="9">Nay when 'tis plain for what is plainer</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-10" n="10">that if you heard you'd be no gainer</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-11" n="11">for sure you are not yet to Learn</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-12" n="12">that hearing is not your Concern</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-13" n="13">then be your Doors no Longer barr'd</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-365-200I-line-14" n="14">your business S<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> is to be heard────<lb/>_Trin Coll: Sat night«LD»P.D</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
